Package pathfinder

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AstarHeuristic
    Interface for all A* heuristic classes
    IGraphSearch
    Any class that can be used to search the graph should implement this class.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AshCrowFlight
    This class is used to calculate the heuristic estimated-cost-to-goal.
    AshManhattan
    This class is used to calculate the heuristic estimated-cost-to-goal.
    Graph
    Objects of this class represents graphs that can be used in games.
    GraphEdge
    This class is used to represent a directed edge between 2 nodes and the cost of traversing this edge.
    GraphNode
    This class represents a node (vertex) that can be used with the Graph class.
    GraphSearch_Astar
    A Star
    Objects of this class are used to search a graph and find a path between two nodes using this algorithm.
    GraphSearch_BFS
    Breadth First Search
    Objects of this class are used to search a graph and find a path between two nodes using this algorithm.
    GraphSearch_DFS
    Depth First Search
    Objects of this class are used to search a graph and find a path between two nodes using this algorithm.
    GraphSearch_Dijkstra
    Dijkstra
    Objects of this class are used to search a graph and find a path between two nodes using this algorithm.
    Message  
    PathFinder
    This is a template class and can be used to start a new processing library or tool.
